{"tid":319091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［黑廉］UGL唔查，fb貼卷廁紙就拉人","createTime":"2017-07-12T14:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T09:56:15.000Z","uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6262cac8457b5f475d133a2d160a8e982f5b883","tid":319091,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:08:51.000Z","msg":"廁紙網站惡搞林鄭　巫堃泰被廉署邀協助調查 | 立場報道 | 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n今年一月，社運人士巫堃泰疑創立惡搞網站「<a href=\"http://carrielam2017.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcarrielam2017.hk&d=ZB%2FJY37%2BBzDAy0yhC9TGJ4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=37f25e49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">carrielam2017.hk</a>」，網頁內只顯示了一卷廁紙，諷刺林鄭月娥的「廁紙門」事件。巫堃泰今日於Facebook稱收到廉署電話，稱希望他協助調查有關網頁為公職選舉而招致選舉開支。<br />\n<br />\n巫堃泰今日在Facebook寫道，下午有廉署調查人員致電他，<a href=\"http://希望他協助調查有關網域名carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%BB%96%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E7%B6%B2%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8Dcarrielam.hk&d=ZB%2FJY37%2BBzDAy0yhC9TGJ4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0fe2a65e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">希望他協助調查有關網域名carrielam.hk</a>及四張於網站展示的相片，為一場公職選舉而招致選舉開支。巫堃泰認為國際人權公約及《香港人權法》均保障港人表達自由，<a href=\"http://又指與carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8F%88%E6%8C%87%E8%88%87carrielam.hk&d=ZB%2FJY37%2BBzDAy0yhC9TGJ4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=35a37a0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">又指與carrielam.hk</a>域名相同稱呼的人，可謂恆河沙數。<br />\n<br />\n他指廉政公署自梁振英成為特首後便被受指責，「我不希望本次事件是另一宗政治調查，令署方與打壓表達自由甚至白色恐怖扯上關係」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://今年一月carrielam.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%88carrielam.hk&d=ZB%2FJY37%2BBzDAy0yhC9TGJ4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=76f01ed6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">今年一月carrielam.hk</a>的網站於網上廣傳，內容只有一頁，就是一大卷廁紙，似是有心人諷刺林鄭的廁紙門醜聞。《立場新聞》記者翻查資料，發現該網的擁有人是巫堃泰。<br />\n<br />\n巫堃泰於香港大學修讀法律系碩士課程，去年參選校務委員會研究生代表選舉，他現在亦是「立言香港」的委員之一。"},{"pid":"51a278857feb19b74f0aebb1a66b58faf44150ff","tid":319091,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:09:21.000Z","msg":"不務正業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7dfeca74ce41bf76c30364a3535e5d146e3ab9d","tid":319091,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"東廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed903788f3a3659de20539daa45e2ec32619394c","tid":319091,"uid":24730,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"個個咁撚關心假龜傳心啲小騙局，東廠林鄭迫害忠良就唔撚理，屌柒你班死港豬，生生世世做中國香港人"},{"pid":"a6587374e9594ecfa0bab0644dabe6e864ea323f","tid":319091,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個咁撚關心假龜傳心啲小騙局，東廠林鄭迫害忠良就唔撚理，屌柒你班死港豬，生生世世做中國香港人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d7c552586105eab6b5668f77ef03015243d7ef","tid":319091,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"香港人係冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01ca09ceb8ff4ed64a009fcff31c694260eaff1","tid":319091,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n<br />\n自己整臭自己個名<br />\n<br />\n同黑警一鳩樣"},{"pid":"78d30c5bb0b7d5500b12ebeb558c778d35d2a516","tid":319091,"uid":101034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"CLS 北韓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c597f736d1e0fa7b4e648cb8bdff0292db8fe2","tid":319091,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"廉處執左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7523f9617ef2d35323ea4a28c24264652dcc65c","tid":319091,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":